dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Wells Ranch quadrangle, San Luis Obispo County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Wells Ranch, CA 1954; DMA 2054 II SW -- Series V895. Photoinspected 1971"
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology (most recent Vedder & Repenning, 1975, modified).
